; DCS-Max: GameDVR Disable Optimization
; ========================================
; Purpose: Disable Windows Game DVR recording to eliminate frame drops
; Default Value: 00000001 (1) - GameDVR enabled
; Optimized Value: 00000000 (0) - GameDVR disabled
; Sources: https://forum.dcs.world/topic/220502-fps-bump-by-disabling-gamedvr-in-windows-10-via-registry/
;          https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0m8Mlvsi6MA&t=18s
